<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.9">
<l>panti rukkum melviralāḷ pāvai paṉimalarāḷ</l>
<l>vanti rukkum mārvaṉnīla mēṉi maṇivaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>anta rattil vāḻumvāṉōr nāyaka ṉāyamainta</l>
<l>vinti raṟkun tamperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He to whose chest has come the girl, she of the dewy blossom,</l>
<l>She with soft fingers who is a relative,</l>
<l rend="indent">he whose blue body is the hue of a sapphire,</l>
<l>Great lord to even Indra who abides as master of the celestials</l>
<l>Who lives in heaven, he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
